snippet.title: OIST Mini Courses
snippet.description:
We are the Graduate School from the Okinawa Institute of Science and Technology (OIST).
Skill Pills are a series of extracurricular intensive nanocourses designed for OIST students, taught by volunteer OIST members and open to all. Some of them will get recorded and uploaded here.
